{
  "texts": [
    "The two datasets are discussed in detail in Sect. 3.",
    "In UrbanSound8K audio dataset we have applied the MFCC feature selection process because of its noise-free samples.",
    "However, in the other dataset, since the samples contain some background noise and other unwanted features, we have applied the STFT feature selection process because MFCCs are sensitive to noise as discussed in the above literature.",
    "After the collection of all the features separately for the two different datasets, we have applied the splitting of datasets into training and testing sets respectively.",
    "After the splitting, the training set contains 80% of the audio samples from the dataset and the testing set contains the remaining randomly selected 20% audio samples for prediction using the trained models."
  ]
}